	.\, We read stories\, sing songs\, and have engaging\, educational activit
	ies that help kids and their caregivers grow together.\n\nEvent Logistics:
	 Our story time portion runs 10:30 - 11:00 AM with open play following aft
	er for 11:00 - 11:30 AM.\, Registration is not required but these programs
	 are very popular and the room capacity can fill up quickly.\, Families of
	 all ages are welcome\, though this early learning program is intended for
