SUMMARY:Stifel Stars on Ice Pre-Show Stargazer Pass
DTSTAMP:20260326T180029Z
DTSTART:20260524T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:THIS IS AN OPTIONAL UPGRADE. TICKET TO THE MAIN EVENT IS ALSO R
	EQUIRED. Pre-Show Stargazer Event takes place prior to Stars on Ice show. 
	Enjoy early entry\, watch the skater warm-ups\, and participate in a Q&A w
	ith several skaters from specified seating sections. Due to this event tak
	ing place prior to doors opening\, EVERYONE entering the venue early must 
	have an event ticket AND Pre-Show Stargazer Pass for entry. This includes 
	all children as well as the parent(s)/guardian(s) wishing to accompany the
	m into the building. If you plan on attending the Pre-Show Stargazer Event
	\, please make sure you have BOTH tickets. NO EXCEPTIONS. Late arrivals wi
	ll not be refunded.\nOPTIONAL UPSELL. NOT VALID FOR EVENT ADMISSION. MUST 
	ALSO HAVE EVENT TICKET! FAN MUST BRING UPSELL TICKET TO EVENT DAY FOR ENTR
	Y. NOTE SPECIFIC PRE-SHOW ACCESS START TIME! STARGAZER PASS TICKET REQUIRE
	D FOR ENTRY.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/stifel-stars-on-ice-preshow-s
